raw_text = "~ start
## 1pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Erika: Knock knock, hansome 🥰
Erika: Guess who got the FUN little task today
Player: Hi Erika
Player: What task?
Erika: The boys get to deside how their girl dresses for the day 😉
Erika: And lucky lucky me, that means YOU get to dress me up 💛
Player: Oh 😳
Erika: Mhmm, I'm currently assigned as \"your girl\"
Erika: Just makes me want to bury your face in my chest 🥰
- I like it [#yellowheart]
	set Story.yellow_heart += 1
	Player: I like it
	Erika: I'm about to faint 🥰
- I guess 😅
	Player: I guess 😅
Erika: I've already tried on some of the outfits I think you'd like hehe
Erika: So tell me... which Erika would you like today? 🤭
Erika: img: erika/18
Erika: Perhaps your professors aren't eye candy enough
Erika: And maybe you'd like to vent the boredom of class on my bed hehe
Erika: Do I look like your personal use nerd?
Erika: Or maybe
Erika: You'd like me to be the girlfriend that turns heads
Erika: Your personal bimbo
Erika: Would you mind if I got a lot of looks while we were on a date?
Erika: Hungry eyes tend to stray hehe
Erika: img: erika/19
Erika: Or you could even wear me 🫦
- The first one
	set Story.flag = \"Erika1A\"
	Player: The first one
	Erika: Ooh, a gentleman 🥰
	Erika: Careful sugar, I might not want it too gentle
- The second one
	set Story.flag = \"Erika1B\"
	Player: The second one
	Erika: Mmmh, good choice 😍
	Erika: A boy who likes attention huh?
Erika: You have no idea how happy this makes me, sweetheart
Erika: A man who actually tells me what he wants 💛
Erika: Maybe we can sneak a quick link behind Jessica's back hehe 🤭
Erika: Anyway! I'm off to slip into your pick
Erika: Take care lover boy 😉
Player: Bye Erika 😀
Erika: 💋
if Story.has_flag(\"Erika1A\"):
	do social_post(\"erika_dressup_nerd\")
if Story.has_flag(\"Erika1B\"):
	do social_post(\"erika_dressup_bimbo\")
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
